import { FormGroup } from "reactstrap";
import "../style.css";
import Cabecalho from "./Cabecalho";
import { Button, Form, Label, Col, Input, Row } from "reactstrap";

const Cadastro = () => {
  return (
    <main>
      <Cabecalho />
      <Form>
        <Row>
          <Col md={6}>
            <FormGroup>
              <Label for="exampleEmail">Email</Label>
              <Input
                id="exampleEmail"
                name="email"
                placeholder="with a placeholder"
                type="email"
              />
            </FormGroup>
          </Col>
          <Col md={6}>
            <FormGroup>
              <Label for="examplePassword">Password</Label>
              <Input
                id="examplePassword"
                name="password"
                placeholder="password placeholder"
                type="password"
              />
            </FormGroup>
          </Col>
        </Row>
        <legend className="col-form-label col-sm-2">Qual seu gÃªnero?</legend>
        <Col sm={10}>
          <FormGroup check>
            <Input name="radio2" type="radio" /> <Label check>Masculino</Label>
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup check>
            <Input name="radio2" type="radio" /> <Label check>Feminino</Label>
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup check>
            <Input name="radio2" type="radio" /> <Label check>Outro</Label>
          </FormGroup>
        </Col>
      </Form>
    </main>
  );
};

export default Cadastro;
